B.LN=new A.aH("Aviation fuel must be free of contaminants before being loaded.","Havac\u0131l\u0131k yak\u0131t\u0131 y\xfcklenmeden \xf6nce kirleticilerden ar\u0131nd\u0131r\u0131lm\u0131\u015f olmal\u0131d\u0131r.","Aviation fuel")
B.XL=s([B.LA,B.LG,B.LN],t.l)
B.Sp=new A.V(B.af,"Articles in Technical Texts",null,B.XL,null,null)
B.Qq=new A.V(B.ag,"\u2708\ufe0f Exam Tip",'Use "an" (not "a") before vowel **sounds** \u2014 not just vowel letters:\n\u2022 **an** ILS approach (I = vowel sound)\n\u2022 **an** RNAV procedure (R = consonant sound, but "RNAV" starts with vowel sound "ar")\n\u2022 **a** NOTAM (N = consonant sound)\n\u2022 **a** VOR (V = consonant sound)\n\nZero article with aviation systems in general context:\n\u2713 "Hydraulic systems are used in \u2026" (NOT "The hydraulic systems")\n\u2713 "ILS provides guidance" (NOT "The ILS provides")',null,null,null)
